{"tid":2411083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與中國清楚區隔！蔡總統指示海巡艦艇塗裝「TAIWAN」","createTime":"2021-02-17T05:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T07:51:13.000Z","uid":50386,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"783e0c3ea5585ba00d7b74bce4ac888cc37607ab","tid":2411083,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FATqZiR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFATqZiR.jpg&h=c5fa7934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對共軍頻頻在台灣海空域附近騷擾，為避免我國艦艇在海上執法過程與中國的船艦混淆，海巡署經指示下，改變海巡艦艇舷側文字塗裝，在現有「R.O.C. COAST GUARD」上方增加醒目「TAIWAN」字樣。對此，總統府發言人張惇涵今日證實，在海巡艦艇上塗裝TAIWAN，「更清楚辨識、更安全執法，正是蔡英文總統的指示。」"},{"pid":"ea37985944add74683ca20bc403df4f1ab337527","tid":2411083,"uid":282930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"小蚑蚑又要心碎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嬲好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"0b1615cb44f84b2945cc57f66d4c564b8c193260","tid":2411083,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:53:29.000Z","msg":"小粉9都係炸少啲好<br />\n<br />\n消委會：1款德國寶和1款億世家氣炸鍋手柄溫度升幅超標<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2410851\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2410851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec17b3e63c49e0d4df1a92550bc8d42849ea18df","tid":2411083,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783e0c3ea5585ba00d7b74bce4ac888cc37607ab","tid":2411083,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FATqZiR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFATqZiR.jpg&h=c5fa7934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對共軍頻頻在台灣海空域附近騷擾，為避免我國艦艇在海上執法過程與中國的船艦混淆，海巡署經指示下，改變海巡艦艇舷側文字塗裝，在現有「R.O.C. COAST GUARD」上方增加醒目「TAIWAN」字樣。對此，總統府發言人張惇涵今日證實，在海巡艦艇上塗裝TAIWAN，「更清楚辨識、更安全執法，正是蔡英文總統的指示。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:56:03.00